### Worker health (checks service=image-compressor on port 8102)
GET {{baseUrl}}/image-compressor/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Compress image — add Backend/http/samples/photo.jpg first (else REST Client shows file error)
POST {{baseUrl}}/image-compressor/compress?quality=82&maxWidth=1920&outputFormat=auto&stripMetadata=true
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=ImageBoundary

--ImageBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="photo.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./samples/photo.jpg
--ImageBoundary--

###

### Compress — WebP output, lower quality
POST {{baseUrl}}/image-compressor/compress?quality=70&maxWidth=1280&outputFormat=webp&stripMetadata=true
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=ImageBoundary

--ImageBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="photo.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./samples/photo.png
--ImageBoundary--

###

### Compress — PNG, max quality
POST {{baseUrl}}/image-compressor/compress?quality=100&outputFormat=png&stripMetadata=false
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=ImageBoundary

--ImageBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="photo.webp"
Content-Type: image/webp

< ./samples/photo.webp
--ImageBoundary--
